Simple dfs: (refer the Trie.java)
    1.
    if(exit condition)
            ....

     for(..)
         dfs(..)

     2.
     result = value;

     for()
        newValue = dfs()
        if()
            result=newValue;

2. 需要理解一下下面的:
Backtracking is a more general purpose algorithm.

Depth-First search is a specific form of backtracking related to searching tree structures.


